Tight-ass.

358
00:24:26,517 --> 00:24:27,957
真是太不尊重人了
So disrespectful.

359
00:24:27,957 --> 00:24:30,144
只要加勒特和法兹切断了组件的链接
Soon as Garrett and Fuzz sever that link...

360
00:24:32,617 --> 00:24:34,457
他就随便我们拿捏了
...he'll be under our control, 

361
00:24:34,457 --> 00:24:36,317
我会和泽弗一起制服他
and I'll take him down with the help of Zeph.

362
00:24:43,957 --> 00:24:45,077
一下搞定
That's what I call a hit.

363
00:24:45,077 --> 00:24:45,597
只需一下
One.

364
00:24:45,597 --> 00:24:47,493
达达·诺尔会被拘留 他的病原体会被没收
Dada Noe and his pathogen will be in custody

365
00:24:47,494 --> 00:24:50,331
这一切会在卖家出现在巴拉姆空间站之前就完成
before the buyers can even show up to the Baraam.

366
00:24:50,737 --> 00:24:52,377
速战速决
And we are in and out.

367
00:24:52,377 --> 00:24:53,637
呃
Mm.

368
00:24:53,637 --> 00:24:55,177
算了
Meh.

369
00:24:56,570 --> 00:24:57,571
啥
Meh?

370
00:24:58,017 --> 00:24:59,817
