743
00:49:15,057 --> 00:49:15,816
分两个队 我会带一个进入树林
Two teams. I'll lead one into the woods.

744
00:49:15,816 --> 00:49:17,117
我带三个人进树林
I'll lead one into the woods.

745
00:49:17,117 --> 00:49:19,597
试试看能不能修好那艘小艇
Three to see if we can salvage that scow.

746
00:49:19,597 --> 00:49:20,737
