You wouldn't bet on a horse named Pretty Certain.

752
00:49:29,416 --> 00:49:33,416
小夸、法兹 你们马上和乔久一起去船
Quas, Fuzz, you get to the scow right away with Georgiou.

753
00:49:33,416 --> 00:49:35,037
泽弗和加勒特 你们跟我待在这
Zeph and Garrett, you stay here with me.

754
00:49:35,037 --> 00:49:36,482
我们会搞定天线阵列的
We'll take care of the antenna array.

755
00:49:36,997 --> 00:49:38,484
请解释一下
Uh, I'm sorry.

756
00:49:38,484 --> 00:49:40,216
我是应该出去
I'm supposed to go out into the woods

757
00:49:40,216 --> 00:49:42,056
