769
00:50:12,357 --> 00:50:14,920
我看这些应该都还能用
Everything I'm seeing should work.

770
00:50:17,156 --> 00:50:19,877
所以我们正在追的东西 天赐之物
So this thing we're chasing, the Godsend,

771
00:50:20,477 --> 00:50:23,477
你的工程师 他们安装保险没有?
your engineers, did they install a fail-safe?

772
00:50:23,477 --> 00:50:25,398
可以远程解除它吗
Can we disable it remotely?

773
00:50:27,677 --> 00:50:29,157
没有这种保险
There is no fail-safe.

774
00:50:29,157 --> 00:50:30,770
我不会允许的
I wouldn't allow it.

775
00:50:30,770 --> 00:50:33,237
不愧是你
How very on-brand for you.

776
00:50:33,237 --> 00:50:34,536
可以再问你一个问题吗
Can I ask you one more question?

777
00:50:34,536 --> 00:50:36,542
真的最后一个问题了
I'm just gonna ask you one more question.

778
00:50:36,542 --> 00:50:39,457
既然你主导了天赐之物的制造
So you brought the Godsend into the world

779
00:50:39,457 --> 00:50:42,597
目的就是抹杀万亿条生命
to vaporize quadrillions of lives.

780
00:50:42,597 --> 00:50:44,337
就从没想过这有点
Never thought that was a little,

781
00:50:44,337 --> 00:50:46,077
太心狠手辣了吗
you know, much?

782
00:50:49,037 --> 00:50:51,457
我早已下令销毁它
I ordered it destroyed.

783
00:50:51,457 --> 00:50:52,977
