Well, your corporate culture was straight-up shit.

786
00:50:57,797 --> 00:50:59,957
而且你还是没回答我的问题
And you didn't answer my question.

787
00:51:00,257 --> 00:51:02,134
渐进线圈不见了
The asymptote coil is gone.

788
00:51:03,736 --> 00:51:06,616
肯定是有人为了铽元素把它拆走了
Someone must have scavenged it for the terbium.

789
00:51:06,616 --> 00:51:09,077
那再找一个 这个东西应该能飞
Well, find another one, this thing should fly.

790
00:51:09,697 --> 00:51:10,917
也许货舱就有
Maybe the cargo hull.

791
00:51:11,497 --> 00:51:12,717
别去
Huh. Oh, no, no.

792
00:51:12,717 --> 00:51:14,696
每个人都待在一起 好吗
Everyone stays together, all right?

793
00:51:15,176 --> 00:51:17,550
降低你杀死我们的可能性
Limits the possibilities of you killing us.

794
00:51:20,117 --> 00:51:21,386
我们去货舱吧
Let's go to the cargo hold, please.

795
00:51:21,387 --> 00:51:23,188
你不来吗
Aren't you coming?

796
00:51:23,736 --> 00:51:26,158
当然 我可太高兴了
Yes. I couldn't be more excited.

797
00:51:29,517 --> 00:51:31,531
当然 我可以下去帮你
Yeah, I could help you down there, of course,

798
00:51:31,531 --> 00:51:33,799
但考虑到 控制我们的行动
but considering how, you know, control

799
00:51:33,799 --> 00:51:36,056
是你整个身份的核心
is central to your entire identity

800
00:51:36,056 --> 00:51:37,803
而我本来就不太能接受这种事
and the fact that I'm just not good at it,

801
00:51:38,357 --> 00:51:39,957
所以我就站在这里 
I'm just gonna stand here 

802
00:51:39,957 --> 00:51:42,741
- 为了我们的关系 什么也不做了 - 那你还真热心呢
- and honor our relationship by doing absolutely nothing. - Helpful.

803
00:51:42,742 --> 00:51:44,443
这叫做彻底的自我接纳
It's called radical self-acceptance.

804
00:51:44,757 --> 00:51:46,237
- 那你真是进步了 - 谢谢夸奖
- Evolved of you. - Well, thank you.

805
00:51:46,237 --> 00:51:47,513
所以说 你能修好它吗？
So, can you fix it?

806
00:51:48,037 --> 00:51:49,997
我甚至不确定它是否坏了
I'm not even sure it's broken.

807
00:51:49,997 --> 00:51:51,584
它只是缺了个零件
It's just missing a part.

808
00:51:51,877 --> 00:51:53,785
看这里 这些被乱扯的线路看着很严重
Look, this-this torn wiring looks dramatic,

809
00:51:53,786 --> 00:51:56,077
但这设备本身就有冗余设计
but this equipment has redundancy built in.

810
00:51:56,077 --> 00:51:57,277
有一个简单的解决办法
There's an easy work-around.

811
00:51:57,277 --> 00:52:00,792
唯一问题是 有人取出了θ节点
Except somebody ripped out the theta junction.

812
00:52:00,793 --> 00:52:03,037
除此之外 这个东西应该可以用
Other than that, this thing should work.

813
00:52:03,037 --> 00:52:05,665
好吧 也许我们的内鬼拿走了它
Okay, well, maybe our mole has it.

814
00:52:10,536 --> 00:52:11,677
加勒特?
Garrett?

815
00:52:11,677 --> 00:52:12,557
咋了
Yeah.

816
00:52:13,157 --> 00:52:14,257
泽弗
Zeph.

817
00:52:14,257 --> 00:52:15,457
泽弗去哪了
Where is Zeph?

818
00:52:23,549 --> 00:52:25,217
泽弗 收到请回复
Zeph, come in.

819
00:52:26,452 --> 00:52:28,688
泽弗 你能听到吗
Zeph, do you copy?

820
00:52:36,028 --> 00:52:37,377
泽弗
Zeph.

821
00:52:46,037 --> 00:52:47,139
加勒特 是你做的吗
Garrett, was that you?

822
00:52:51,157 --> 00:52:52,778
加勒特 刚刚那是什么情况
Garrett, what the hell was that?

823
00:52:52,778 --> 00:52:54,536
有人刚激活了天线阵列
Someone just activated the antenna array.

824
