该死
Damn it.

825
00:52:56,897 --> 00:52:57,877
具体情况如何
What's happening?

826
00:52:59,457 --> 00:53:01,196
加勒特 情况简报
Garrett, sitrep.

827
00:53:02,257 --> 00:53:03,989
越来越棒了
This is going to be good.

828
00:53:03,989 --> 00:53:06,859
上尉 收到请回复 完毕
Lieutenant, do you copy? Over.

829
00:53:15,557 --> 00:53:16,296
安全
Clear.

830
00:53:17,457 --> 00:53:18,197
安全
Clear.

831
00:53:18,897 --> 00:53:20,171
这里什么都没有
Nothing here.

832
00:53:20,172 --> 00:53:22,497
怎么会有人用这个来发出信号呢
How could someone have used this to send out a signal?

833
00:53:22,977 --> 00:53:25,157
不可能 它少了一个部件
Impossible. It's missing a part.

834
00:53:25,677 --> 00:53:27,576
有人把它打成了筛子
And someone shot it to hell.

835
00:53:27,576 --> 00:53:28,637
我听到有人在跑
I heard someone running.

836
00:53:29,277 --> 00:53:31,176
泽弗一定是把θ节点放回去了
Zeph must have put the theta junction back in.

837
00:53:31,496 --> 00:53:33,237
使用完毕后 射击毁掉了阵列
Then shot it after he used the array.

838
00:53:37,016 --> 00:53:39,457
所以他肯定是在擅离职守后绕回来的
So he must have circled back after he went AWOL.

839
00:53:40,017 --> 00:53:42,977
泽弗来这个星球来阻碍我们
Zeph came down to this planet to sabotage us.

840
00:53:44,129 --> 00:53:45,898
现在我们被困住了
And now that we're stranded,

841
00:53:45,898 --> 00:53:48,776
他用阵列给同谋发了信息
he sent a message to whoever he's working with.

842
00:53:48,776 --> 00:53:50,435
他会潜伏直到撤离的船抵达
And he'll lay low until his ride gets here,

843
00:53:50,435 --> 00:53:52,517
然后溜之大吉
and then he's long gone.

844
00:53:52,517 --> 00:53:54,197
那我们得先找到他
Then we need to find him first.

845
00:54:03,137 --> 00:54:04,737
观察者 能收到吗
Observer, do you copy?

846
00:54:04,737 --> 00:54:07,085
拜托 突袭者一号 我什么时候收不到了
Please, Raider One, when do I not copy?

847
