850
00:54:14,817 --> 00:54:16,996
就在这个区域 完毕
was just in this sector. Over.

851
00:54:17,897 --> 00:54:21,000
收到 保持低调 保持队形
Copy. Stay low and tight, people.

852
00:54:25,037 --> 00:54:27,077
你曾效力的那个军阀 吉里
The warlord you served, Giri,

853
00:54:27,077 --> 00:54:28,017
她后来怎样了
what happened to her?

854
00:54:28,784 --> 00:54:30,257
她死了 死于生前最爱的事
She died like she lived.

855
00:54:30,257 --> 00:54:32,144
你知道我说的什么
By that, you know what I mean.

856
00:54:33,137 --> 00:54:33,917
她很幸运
She was lucky.

857
00:54:33,917 --> 00:54:35,757
没染上良心这种东西
She wasn't infected with a conscience.

858
00:54:35,757 --> 00:54:36,657
染上?
Infected?

