克里米亚-刚果出血热
Crimean-Congo Hemorrhagic Fever...

895
00:56:32,797 --> 00:56:35,197
你要哭着念完19万孩子的名字吗
Are you gonna sob out 190,000 names?

896
00:56:35,197 --> 00:56:37,377
你怎么能这么冷漠 如此无情
How can you be so cold and insensitive?

897
00:56:37,377 --> 00:56:39,016
