Except the footage was probably murdered along with him.

900
00:56:42,557 --> 00:56:45,197
我们可以将三录仪连接到外骨骼装甲上
We could connect one of the tricorders to his suit.

901
00:56:45,517 --> 00:56:46,776
就算没剩多少数据
Whatever data is left,

902
00:56:46,776 --> 00:56:48,177
凶手也昭然若揭了
we'll know who did this.

903
00:56:48,177 --> 00:56:50,997
说得好像我们都是嫌疑人一样
You say that like we're all suspects.

904
00:56:50,997 --> 00:56:52,696
并不是 好吗
We're not. All right?

905
00:56:52,696 --> 00:56:56,097
那时候我 法兹和乔久都在那艘船里
Fuzz, me and her were in the scow when all this happened--

906
00:56:56,097 --> 00:56:58,157
每个人都在彼此的视线范围内
everyone in sight of everyone else.

907
00:56:58,157 --> 00:57:00,692
没一个人乱跑 没错吧
And nobody went anywhere, right?

908
00:57:01,717 --> 00:57:02,808
对啊
Right.

909
00:57:05,557 --> 00:57:08,616
这不是泽弗的
Oh, this is not Zeph's.

910
00:57:09,557 --> 00:57:12,357
深褐色头发 25厘米
Brunette. 25 centimeters.

