00:57:32,917 --> 00:57:34,696
行 所以你喜欢机甲什么的
Okay, so you're into mecha boom-boom.

915
00:57:34,696 --> 00:57:36,495
很多人类都是 不必害羞
Lots of humans are. No shame.

916
00:57:40,577 --> 00:57:41,816
<i>检测到血液</i>

917
00:57:43,496 --> 00:57:44,677
呃 那不可能啊
Well, that's impossible.

918
00:58:02,457 --> 00:58:04,056
加勒特上尉
Lieutenant Garrett,

919
00:57:58,000 --> 00:57:59,379
<i>痕迹匹配</i>

920
00:58:04,056 --> 00:58:06,926
为什么你的指甲缝里会有泽弗的血
why is Zeph's blood underneath your fingernails?

921
00:58:12,117 --> 00:58:13,557
加勒特上尉
Lieutenant Garrett,

922
00:58:13,557 --> 00:58:16,897
在泽弗的尸体上发现了你的证据
evidence from you was found on Zeph's body,

923
00:58:16,897 --> 00:58:19,837
泽弗尸体上的证据也在你身上发现了
and evidence from Zeph's body was found on you.

924
00:58:20,517 --> 00:58:22,157
不像星际舰队的作风啊
Not very Starfleet.

925
00:58:22,157 --> 00:58:23,708
我问心无愧
Oh, I am very Starfleet.

926
00:58:24,337 --> 00:58:25,917
你清楚凶手并不是我
And you know I didn't do this.

927
00:58:26,997 --> 00:58:29,882
你只是害怕任何有道德准则的人
You are just terrified of anyone with a moral compass.

928
00:58:31,283 --> 00:58:35,120
但在那颗纯洁的小心灵的深处
And deep down in that pure little heart,

929
00:58:36,056 --> 00:58:38,817
你其实是个混乱小妖精 没错吧
you're actually a chaos goblin, aren't you?

930
00:58:38,817 --> 00:58:40,897
- 我知道你是这样的 小天使  - 别这么叫我
- I know you have it in you, angel. - Don't call me that.

931
00:58:40,897 --> 00:58:42,897
星际舰队发现了这样的你
Starfleet sniffed you out

932
00:58:42,897 --> 00:58:45,656
把你放在了最能发挥你作用的地方
and put you in a place where you'd be most useful.

933
00:58:45,656 --> 00:58:48,597
31区正是为那些打破规则
Section 31 is just the place for officers 

934
00:58:48,597 --> 00:58:53,197
却又从未真正越界的军官准备的地方
who bend the rules, never quite break them until they do.

935
00:58:53,197 --> 00:58:56,741
而你 正好适合这里
And you fit right in here.

936
00:59:02,097 --> 00:59:03,557
你想怎么折磨我都可以
You can torture me all you want.

937
00:59:03,557 --> 00:59:05,985
但我坚持自己没杀过人
You will never make me a murderer.

938
00:59:07,452 --> 00:59:08,497
住手
No.

939
00:59:23,336 --> 00:59:24,904
我们拿到录像了
We've got footage!

940
00:59:28,657 --> 00:59:29,457
住手
Stop!

941
00:59:29,816 --> 00:59:31,110
快住手
Stop!

942
00:59:33,045 --> 00:59:34,616
这是我的装甲
This is my suit.

943
00:59:34,616 --> 00:59:36,781
我即是装甲！
I am the suit!

944
00:59:37,883 --> 00:59:40,251
装甲就是我！
The suit is me!

945
00:59:40,252 --> 00:59:41,786
等一下
One second.

946
00:59:45,290 --> 00:59:46,977
我们是你的朋友
We were your friends.

947
00:59:47,736 --> 00:59:48,997
曾是你的朋友
We were your friends.

948
00:59:49,896 --> 00:59:51,729
你杀不了我
You can't kill me.

949
00:59:51,730 --> 00:59:52,497
泽弗 别
Zeph, no.

950
00:59:52,497 --> 00:59:53,557
你不能
You can't kill...

951
00:59:59,637 --> 01:00:01,357
泽弗是自杀的?
Zeph killed himself?

952
01:00:01,997 --> 01:00:03,108
他为什么要这么做
Why would he do that?

953
01:00:04,677 --> 01:00:07,997
抱歉让您失望了 陛下
Sorry to disappoint you, Your Majesty.

954
01:00:09,637 --> 01:00:11,736
这一切根本说不通
Look, none of this is making any sense.

955
01:00:11,736 --> 01:00:13,096
是啊 非常之不合理
No, none of it makes a lick of sense.

956
01:00:13,096 --> 01:00:14,536
他为什么要这样做呢
Why would he do this?

957
01:00:15,037 --> 01:00:16,257
给我几分钟时间
Give me a couple minutes to...

958
01:00:16,257 --> 01:00:17,197
我们没时间了
We don't have minutes.

959
01:00:17,197 --> 01:00:19,158
那就几秒钟行了没
Well, then give me a couple seconds, then.

960
01:00:22,037 --> 01:00:22,917
可能是你
Could be you.

961
01:00:22,917 --> 01:00:23,697
原话奉还
Could be you.

962
01:00:23,697 --> 01:00:25,197
但我连你长什么样都不知道
And I still don't even know what you look like.

963
01:00:25,197 --> 01:00:27,157
你可以变成任何你想变的样子
You could change into anything you want.

964
01:00:27,157 --> 01:00:28,696
她是新来的 她才不在乎我们
She's new. She doesn't care about us.

965
01:00:28,696 --> 01:00:29,637
我可是星际舰队的军官
I'm Starfleet.

966
01:00:30,337 --> 01:00:32,216
当你在说我这套装甲的时候
When you are talking about the suit,

967
01:00:32,725 --> 01:00:34,317
就是在说我
you're talking about Zeph.

968
01:00:34,317 --> 01:00:35,496
这可不是法兹
This isn't Fuzz.

969
01:00:35,496 --> 01:00:37,275
这个瓦肯外表不过是台机器
The Vulcan's just a machine, you know.

970
01:00:37,276 --> 01:00:38,809
我在里面呢
I'm inside.

971
01:00:38,810 --> 01:00:40,477
这是身材羞辱
Scale-shamer!

972
01:00:40,477 --> 01:00:43,457
你绝对想不到我能进入多小的地方
You wouldn't believe the tiny spots I can get into.

973
01:00:43,457 --> 01:00:48,152
比如 身体改造组件的内部空间
For example, the inner workings of body modifications.

974
01:00:48,153 --> 01:00:49,976
当时他启用了自动驾驶
There's an autopilot.

975
01:00:49,976 --> 01:00:52,257
这是唯一合理的解释
That's the only thing that makes sense.

976
01:00:54,077 --> 01:00:58,230
你给瓦肯机器设定了自动驾驶程序
You set the Vulcan machine on autopilot.

977
01:00:59,731 --> 01:01:03,467
所以当时它的反应才那么古怪
That's why its responses were so strange.

978
01:01:04,317 --> 01:01:05,237
你来不来
Aren't you coming?

979
01:01:05,697 --> 01:01:06,617
当然
Yes.

980
01:01:08,417 --> 01:01:11,475
你钻进了泽弗的外骨骼装甲
You flew into Zeph's exoskeleton.

981
01:01:12,117 --> 01:01:13,837
你钻进去之后
And once you were inside...

982
01:01:13,837 --> 01:01:15,777
有人把西塔接口拆掉了
Somebody ripped out  the theta junction.

983
01:01:15,777 --> 01:01:17,237
加勒特 泽弗去哪了
Garrett, where's Zeph?

984
01:01:19,051 --> 01:01:21,637
然后你控制了泽弗的装甲
Then you took control of Zeph's suit.

985
01:01:23,357 --> 01:01:25,637
当别人在找他的时候
While the others were out looking for him,

986
01:01:25,637 --> 01:01:27,858
你控制他溜回了通讯阵列
you made him sneak back into the antenna array

987
01:01:27,859 --> 01:01:29,496
然后发送了那些信息
and send those messages.

988
01:01:30,536 --> 01:01:32,296
不要这么做
Don't do this to them!

989
01:01:32,897 --> 01:01:34,577
我们是你的朋友啊
We were your friends.

990
01:01:34,577 --> 01:01:37,368
然后你销毁了所有证据
Then you destroyed the evidence.

991
01:01:37,677 --> 01:01:38,903
还杀掉了泽弗
And you killed Zeph.

992
01:01:41,117 --> 01:01:43,037
然后你再把这一切嫁祸给加勒特
And then you planted the evidence on Garrett here.

993
01:01:48,022 --> 01:01:49,557
举起手来 法兹
Hands up, Fuzz.

994
01:01:49,557 --> 01:01:52,117
真是倒了血霉了
Oh, shite and ever shite.

995
01:01:59,457 --> 01:02:02,257
阿洛克 你不会真的要信她的鬼话吧
You're honestly gonna believe what she says, Alok?

996
01:02:02,257 --> 01:02:04,437
夸西 我们一起经历了这么多 你也信她的话吗
Quasi, after everything we've been through?

997
01:02:06,998 --> 01:02:09,668
我能先说一句吗
C-Can I just say one thing first?

998
01:02:14,797 --> 01:02:16,541
泽弗的外骨骼我还控制着呢
I'm still hacked into Zeph's exoskeleton.

999
01:02:30,255 --> 01:02:31,256
喂
Come on!

1000
01:02:36,097 --> 01:02:38,330
说好的「不抛弃任何人」呢
What happened to "no crew member left behind"?

1001
01:02:55,917 --> 01:02:57,357
快一点啊
Come on, come on!

1002
01:02:57,357 --> 01:02:58,383
靠近他们
Get us closer.

1003
01:04:09,496 --> 01:04:11,557
接住你了
I got you. I got you.

1004
01:04:11,557 --> 01:04:12,877
还好有我
Nice and easy.

1005
01:04:12,877 --> 01:04:13,736
该死
Damn.

1006
01:05:12,551 --> 01:05:15,197
你很关注黑市的动向 没错吧
You keep tabs on the black market, hmm?

1007
01:05:15,197 --> 01:05:16,997
你就是在那听说天赐之物的消息的
And that's where you heard about the Godsend.

1008
01:05:16,997 --> 01:05:18,357
你在乎这些干什么
Why do you care?

1009
01:05:18,357 --> 01:05:20,124
家人你都下得去手
You killed your family.

1010
01:05:20,124 --> 01:05:21,793
再多点人算什么呢
What's a few billion more people, huh?

1011
01:05:22,536 --> 01:05:25,016
天赐之物在哪 你的同谋是谁
Where is it? And who are you working with?

1012
01:05:25,016 --> 01:05:26,397
你登上了皇位
You took your crown

1013
01:05:26,397 --> 01:05:29,701
他们却痛苦地死在你的脚边
while they died in agony not ten feet away.

1014
01:05:30,797 --> 01:05:34,117
你奴役了你唯一的朋友
You condemned your only friend to slavery,

1015
01:05:34,117 --> 01:05:37,441
居然还有脸在最后一刻给他一些怜悯?
and then you had the balls to offer him kindness at the end?

1016
01:05:39,717 --> 01:05:41,513
你怎么会知道的
How could you know that?

1017
01:05:41,997 --> 01:05:44,017
你终于发现了
Glad you're catching on.

1018
01:05:44,017 --> 01:05:46,285
他把你耍了 女皇陛下
He played you, Emperor.

1019
01:05:46,677 --> 01:05:48,320
桑还活着
San's alive.

1020
01:05:53,157 --> 01:05:55,460
不可能
It's not possible.

1021
01:05:57,717 --> 01:05:59,016
绝对不可能 到底怎么回事
That's not possible. How?

1022
01:05:59,016 --> 01:06:01,833
他训练出了对毒药的抗药性
He built up an immunity from that poison, you know.

1023
01:06:01,833 --> 01:06:05,003
每次只多服用很小的剂量
Teeny tiny doses over time.

1024
01:06:06,271 --> 01:06:10,056
看样子是小混蛋又赢了一次
Once again, small shite for the win, mama.

1025
01:06:11,016 --> 01:06:12,897
他在哪
Where is he?!

1026
01:06:13,297 --> 01:06:15,096
期待他的精彩表演吧
He's gonna put on quite the show.

1027
01:06:15,877 --> 01:06:17,656
你制造了天赐之物
You built the Godsend.

1028
01:06:17,656 --> 01:06:19,576
你制造了一个怪物
You made this monster.

1029
01:06:19,576 --> 01:06:21,486
全是因为你
This is all you.

1030
01:07:05,496 --> 01:07:07,664
小心点可以吗
Be careful, all right?

1031
01:07:08,317 --> 01:07:10,317
我让你小心点
I said be careful.

1032
01:07:10,317 --> 01:07:12,296
我还得用它活动呢
I have to get around in that.

1033
01:07:15,949 --> 01:07:17,742
你都能买得起一百多具身体了 还在乎这一具
You can afford a hundred of them now.

1034
01:07:17,742 --> 01:07:18,943
太好了
Oh, great.

1035
01:07:19,637 --> 01:07:21,597
这个能用不就行了
I'd settle for one that works.

1036
01:07:23,416 --> 01:07:25,277
所以就是这个
So that's it?

1037
01:07:25,277 --> 01:07:26,797
无敌的天赐之物
The almighty Godsend.

1038
01:07:26,797 --> 01:07:28,277
等你做上皇帝了
When you're emperor,

1039
01:07:28,277 --> 01:07:31,917
能不能给它换个没那么奇怪的名字
maybe start by naming it something less confusing.

1040
01:07:37,200 --> 01:07:40,099
<i>离子风暴会聚倒计时</i>

1041
01:07:45,816 --> 01:07:47,405
跨越两个宇宙的通道打开时
Once that passageway opens up,

1042
01:07:47,406 --> 01:07:50,477
他会联系人族 他们会从中进入
he contacts the Terrans, they come through.

1043
01:07:53,037 --> 01:07:54,578
然后他们会在此引爆
They're detonating it here.

1044
01:07:55,157 --> 01:07:57,857
他就会成为帝国的新宠
And he'd be the darling of the Empire.

1045
01:07:57,857 --> 01:08:00,616
发生这样的灾难 星联就会陷入混乱
So he throws the Federation into chaos...

1046
01:08:00,616 --> 01:08:02,696
星际舰队自顾不暇
Starfleet will start scrambling.

1047
01:08:02,696 --> 01:08:04,255
入侵的完美时机
Perfect time to invade.

1048
01:08:07,537 --> 01:08:08,817
你创造了它
You gave birth to this thing.

1049
01:08:10,877 --> 01:08:12,317
我们要如何阻止
How do we stop it?

1050
01:08:12,317 --> 01:08:13,377
没办法
We don't.

1051
01:08:13,377 --> 01:08:15,816
我们被困在这 追不上他
We're trapped here, so we can't follow him.

1052
01:08:15,816 --> 01:08:17,997
通讯天线坏了 我们也无法警告任何人
The antenna's destroyed, so we can't warn anybody.

1053
01:08:17,997 --> 01:08:19,303
胡扯
That is bullshit.

1054
01:08:20,817 --> 01:08:21,736
你肯定有更好的办法
You can do better than that.

1055
01:08:21,736 --> 01:08:22,507
我做不到
I can't.

1056
01:08:22,877 --> 01:08:23,937
天赐之物就像我自己
The Godsend is me.

1057
01:08:23,937 --> 01:08:25,917
我唯一无法战胜的就是自己
I'm the only one I could never defeat.

1058
01:08:29,677 --> 01:08:31,650
过去总是缠着你不放
The past always catches up with you.

1059
01:08:32,317 --> 01:08:33,096
不是吗
Right?

1060
01:08:37,377 --> 01:08:39,157
但并不意味着它总能赢
Doesn't mean it always wins.

1061
01:08:42,117 --> 01:08:44,262
每个安全屋都有备用计划
Every safe house, I have a backup plan.

1062
01:08:44,262 --> 01:08:45,717
把那艘垃圾船修好
We'll get that scow running.

1063
01:08:46,157 --> 01:08:49,133
老大 那家伙飞不起来的
Boss, the scow won't fly.

1064
01:08:49,517 --> 01:08:50,977
没有渐进线圈就不可能
Not without an asymptote coil.

1065
01:08:52,877 --> 01:08:54,573
我们有一个
We have one.

1066
01:08:54,573 --> 01:08:56,475
我们必须追上桑
We'll catch up with San.

1067
01:08:56,475 --> 01:08:58,017
我们要阻止他联系人族帝国
We'll make sure he can't contact the Terrans.

1068
01:08:59,157 --> 01:09:00,479
你早把线圈拆出来了
You ripped out the coil.

1069
01:09:00,479 --> 01:09:02,847
有内奸在 我可没法什么都说出来
Couldn't tell you while a mole was still running around.

1070
01:09:05,850 --> 01:09:07,686
你个混蛋
Asshole.

1071
01:09:20,298 --> 01:09:22,734
小夸 去帮她一下
Okay, Quas, give her a rip.

1072
01:09:28,557 --> 01:09:29,758
还是只有一下反应
Still just one pulse.

1073
01:09:35,797 --> 01:09:36,815
来活了 朋友们
And we're in business.

1074
01:09:36,815 --> 01:09:40,497
我们只有不到三十分钟时间
Okay, team, we have less than 30 minutes.

1075
01:09:40,497 --> 01:09:42,437
小夸 设定航线前往新月星云
Quas, set a course for the Crescent Nebula.

1076
01:09:42,437 --> 01:09:45,037
路上将会非常颠簸
All right, this is gonna be bumpy and bad.

1077
01:09:45,037 --> 01:09:47,077
我推测桑的星舰会有武器
I'm assuming San's ship will be armed.

1078
01:09:47,077 --> 01:09:48,917
废话 人族帝国能有不武装的星舰吗
Yeah, every Terran ship's armed.

1079
01:09:49,357 --> 01:09:52,317
对方有质子加农炮 鱼雷
He'll have proton cannons, torpedoes,

1080
01:09:52,317 --> 01:09:54,933
而我们只有一堆垃圾
and we are a garbage barge.

1081
01:09:55,697 --> 01:09:56,601
有啥好笑的
Why are you laughing?

1082
01:09:56,601 --> 01:09:58,737
因为我想不出来还有什么更糟的情况了
Because I can't imagine things getting much worse.

1083
01:10:04,837 --> 01:10:05,676
出发
Let's go.

1084
01:10:16,037 --> 01:10:18,355
所以 这艘船会在自身周围制造牵引力场
So, this thing flies around in the middle of a tractor field.

1085
01:10:18,356 --> 01:10:20,557
人们向太空里面扔垃圾
People jettison their garbage into space,

1086
01:10:20,557 --> 01:10:22,637
然后这种驳船会拖着垃圾和力场
and the scow flies around and drags the trash

1087
01:10:22,637 --> 01:10:23,657
一起飞行
along with the field.

1088
01:10:24,596 --> 01:10:26,677
牵引力场里塞满垃圾之后
Once the tractor field is full,

1089
01:10:26,677 --> 01:10:28,497
就会一起把垃圾甩进星云里
it dumps the trash in the Nebula

1090
01:10:28,497 --> 01:10:30,277
让垃圾在辐射里自行分解
where it disintegrates in the radiation.

1091
01:10:31,277 --> 01:10:32,197
我就是想确认一下
I just want to be clear.

1092
01:10:32,197 --> 01:10:34,297
你是说我们最有可能用的上的武器
You're saying that our best potential weapon is

1093
01:10:34,297 --> 01:10:35,897
是用来拖垃圾的牵引光束吗
a beam for collecting garbage?

1094
01:10:35,897 --> 01:10:36,697
没错
Yes.

1095
01:10:36,697 --> 01:10:37,297
那太棒了
Great.

1096
01:10:37,297 --> 01:10:39,844
提醒下 你在那指手画脚帮不上一点忙
Hey, being judgy never helped anything.

1097
01:10:41,997 --> 01:10:42,897
你要去哪
Where are you going?

1098
01:10:42,897 --> 01:10:43,797
轮机室
